Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{It's because you showed up...}Chỉ vì cậu xuất hiện...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{What is?}Cái gì cơ?
